## ğŸš€ Getting Started

### Requirements

- [Power BI Desktop](https://powerbi.microsoft.com/) (latest version recommended)

### How to Open

1. Clone or download this repository.
2. Open `The Film Library.pbix` using Power BI Desktop.
3. Review or refresh the data (if source is external).
4. Customize or publish the report to the Power BI Service if needed.

## ğŸ“Œ Features

- Interactive filters and slicers for year, genre, rating, etc.
- Dynamic tooltips and bookmarks.
- Clean and modern visual layout.
- Designed for both business stakeholders and data analysts.

## ğŸ› ï¸ Customization

To adapt the dashboard to your own data:

- Replace the data source via **Transform Data > Data Source Settings**.
- Modify visuals or DAX measures to suit your metrics.
- Add new pages or KPIs as needed.

